## Terminal goal — VIROCAPSID row in 16-cell matrix

VIROCAPSID 은 4 disease class 각각 VLP / cage 구조 design. Meta `.roadmap.hexa_bio` §0 의 **V 행**.

| Cell  | Disease       | 후보 cage (예)                                          |
|-------|---------------|----------------------------------------------------------|
| V·α   | AML           | neoantigen-display 종양 백신 VLP                         |
| V·β   | SCD           | HSC 표적 AAV-like gene-cage                              |
| V·γ   | pan-cov       | 다가 VLP 백신 (multi-spike variants)                     |
| V·δ   | senolytic     | senolytic payload 캡슐                                   |

**Cell DoD**: in-silico cage design + σ(6)=12 STRUCTURAL-EXACT (T=1) 또는 calibrated (T>1) + nucleation-elongation yield ≥0.85 + witness → `state/discovery_absorption/registry.jsonl`.

