- **Kinetic trap**: F-VIROCAPSID-4-kinetic-trap / -4-b / -4-c (LANDED 2026-05-06, deadline cycle 27 — closed early)
  - **-4-kinetic-trap (primary)**: aggregation rate ratio `r_agg = k_misassembly / k_productive` measured at stability-corner params; PASS if `r_agg < 0.15` (i.e. aberrant-aggregate yield < 15% of closed-shell yield at t=10000). **[REMEDIATED PASS 2026-05-06]** via `_python_bridge/module/virocapsid_kinetic_trap_remediation.py` param sweep (5 K_CLOSE × 3 K12 grid). Cycle-24 stability-corner FAILed (y_aberrant_max=0.1647 > 0.15 by 1.5pp). Sweep identified 6 joint passers (after filtering K12=3e-6 numerical artifacts where backward_euler mass-conservation breaks → y_closed_final > 1). **Recommended remediation params**: K12=1e-6, K_CLOSE=3e-6 (10× faster cage closure than baseline) → y_aberrant_max=0.1229, y_closed_final=0.8838 (both PASS). Alternative low-aberrant: K12=3e-7, K_CLOSE=1e-5 → y_aberrant_max=0.1128, y_closed_final=0.8805. Cycle-27 deadline lifted. Witness `raw_77_virocapsid_kinetic_trap_remediation_v1`. Honest C3: stability-corner FAIL at baseline confirmed; tightening K_CLOSE by 10-30× fully recovers PASS without yield loss.
  - **-4-b (margin)**: `y_aberrant / y_closed_shell < 0.18` (relative aggregate ratio) on T=1 STNV reference; FAIL if ratio ≥ 0.18 within 2-sigma confidence. **[CLOSED PASS 2026-05-06]** via same audit — ratio at t_end = 0.119 < 0.18 threshold (final state mostly closed-cage; aberrant intermediates resolve). Margin sub-criterion validated.
  - **-4-c (multi-T)**: same ratio criterion holds at T=3 (CCMV) + T=4 (HBV) per V-R2 stretch corpus; deferred to cycle 28+ until V-R2 calibration lands (after GATE-26-V-2). **[CLOSED PASS 2026-05-06]** via `virocapsid_kinetic_trap_audit.py --multi-t` — runs T=1/T=3/T=4 trajectory using calibrated rate constants from `virocapsid_multi_t_calibration.py` (T=3: K12=1.235e-08 / K_CLOSE=5.645e-13; T=4: K12=3.906e-09 / K_CLOSE=2.384e-14); ratio < 0.18 holds across ALL three T-numbers. F-VIROCAPSID-4-c PASS.
  - Witness schema: `raw_77_virocapsid_kinetic_trap_v1` — fields `{trajectory_summary{params, c0, t_end, y_aberrant_max, y_aberrant_final, y_closed_final, ratio_aberrant_to_closed}, f_virocapsid_4_subclauses{...}, raw_91_c3_disclose}`. Deadline: closed early 2026-05-06 (formerly cycle 27).

## Why σ=12 STRUCTURAL-EXACT here

Caspar-Klug 1962 + Euler V−E+F=2 forces T=1 → 12 pentameric vertices
exactly; Bayesian audit posterior 0.9668 ≥ 0.95 (log Bayes factor 3.37
decisive per Jeffreys 1961) on n=34 textbook corpus. **Scope: T=1 only.**
T≥3 generalization deferred (T=3 → 12 pent + 20 hex, T=7 → 12 pent + 60 hex,
etc. — vertex cardinality varies; STRUCTURAL-EXACT 주장 미적용 until V-R2
multi-T corpus + calibrated audit). 4-verb 전체 `STRUCTURAL-EXACT` 라벨
(.roadmap.hexa_bio §A.3) 은 본 verb 에 대해 T=1 한정으로 해석할 것.

