- **novel AAV capsid tissue-tropism** — cardiotropic AAV6/9 (mi) / lung-tropic (lung_normalization) / hair-follicle (alopecia)
- **viral capsid kinetic-trap audit** — novel capsid 의 self-assembly stability (F-VIROCAPSID-3 cycle 31)
- **icosahedral T=1 60-subunit cage** — novel vaccine antigen presentation
- COVID-class antiviral cross-link: F-Q-6-B-real-nirmatrelvir-vqe (cycle 97 sub-µHa) + viral RNA cleavage RIBOZYME axis

### Representative falsifier (novel drug 기준)

| ID                  | scope (novel drug context)                                |
|---------------------|----------------------------------------------------------|
| F-novel-ca-V-N      | mRNA-LNP neoantigen vaccine for hxq-ca-* (BNT122-class)   |
| F-novel-al-V-N      | follicle stem-cell mRNA-LNP gene therapy for hxq-al-*     |
| F-novel-mi-V-N      | cardiotropic AAV6/9 delivery for hxq-mi-*                 |
| F-novel-ln-V-N      | lung-tropic mRNA-LNP / AAV (CFTR/COVID/IPF) for hxq-ln-*  |
