### Phase plan (novel drug 기준)

- Phase α: each disease 의 hxq-* 의 delivery modality 결정 (mRNA-LNP vs AAV vs naked)
- Phase β: novel capsid / LNP encapsulation efficiency > threshold
- Phase γ: tissue-selectivity in vitro / mock-cell pilot
- Phase δ: cross-axis Stage 3 — hxq-* + VIROCAPSID delivery + RIBOZYME mechanism
